'''Fahla''' was a specially bred [[Sensor/Legends|sensor]]-dampening water [[Plant/Legends|plant]] created by the infamous [[Ho'Din/Legends|Ho'Din]] terrorist [[Ort Hoogra-D'En]].

Fahla blinded sensors that detected large quantities of metal and energy, the main components of vehicles and bases.

Fahla required large amounts of [[Water/Legends|water]] to prosper, so fahla groves had to be placed in lakes, large pools, oceans, or other large bodies of water to be effective. To mask a specific area, twice that area in fahla plants had to be present. The only source of fahla was the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Pallaxides]] around Hoogra-D'En's secret base. It is unknown if any samples of fahla ever made it offworld to other planets.

